[SN]TITLE[SN]
How to put an elephant to sleep

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Fitting a tracker on a large elephant is a risky operation. First a vet has to find a safe place to dart it with anaesthetic, then the team has to work quickly attach the collar.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
31 August 2016 Last updated at 15:01 BST
Elephants Without Borders is working with southern Africa governments to monitor and protect the animals that wander across Botswana, Namibia, Angola, Zambia and Zimbabwe.
The BBC's Alastair Leithead reports.
